                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9112" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1380</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1151 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合法性接纳：国资助力禾大科技数字农业营销之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Acceptance of Legitimacy: State-Owned Capital Empower Heda Technology&#39;s Digital Agriculture Marketing Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">戴鑫，陈碧莎，张佳龙，黄锐扬，罗其斌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉禾大科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字农业；组织合法性；合法性策略；2G 营销；2B 营销；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital Agriculture; Organizational Legitimacy; LegitimacyStrategies; B2G Marketing; B2B Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015 年，为了响应国家政策号召，禾大科技走上了探索数字农业发展的道路。“卖什么”、“卖给谁”是当时新兴的农业科技企业面临的关键问题。十年间，禾大科技始终致力于解决这两个关键问题。创业初期，禾大科技开发的“田小二”APP 和测土配肥服务推广遇阻。2019 年，国有资本的进入为禾大科技带来了资金、战略方向、管理人才、产业资源和信用背书等支持。随后，禾大科技推出智能灌溉解决方案，进入成长阶段。2022 年，禾大科技针对农民劳动强度大的痛点，开发数字化灌溉控制系统和自研球阀，面向政府、种田大户、农业种植企业等多个对象展开营销，产品得到政府认可并被写入规范性文件，同时吸引了国有资本的新一轮投资。如今，禾大科技的数字农业服务在新疆取得成功，并准备拓展中亚、中东市场，助力“一带一路”建设。禾大科技从缺乏市场认可到被政府客户接受，再从政府买单到农户接纳，先后获得了来自政府、种田大户、农业种植企业等多个主体的认可，为我们展现了国资助力农业科技企业获得合法性生存的营销之道。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2015, in response to the national policy initiative, Heda Technology embarked on the road of exploring digital agriculture development. &quot;What to sell&quot; and &quot;Who will buy&quot; were the key issues facing the emerging agricultural technology enterprises at that time Over the course of a decade, Heda Technology consistently dedicated itself to addressing these two pivotal issues. At the beginning of the venture, Heda developed the soil data platform &quot;Field Helper&quot;, but the results fell short of expectations. In 2019, the entry of state-owned capital brought support such as capital, strategic direction, management talent, industrial resources and credit endorsement to HeDa Technology. Subsequently, HeDa Technology launched smart irrigation solutions and entered the growth stage. In 2022, HeDa Technology developed a digital irrigation control system and self-developed ball valves to address the pain point of farmers&#39; high labour intensity, and marketed them to a wide range of targets, including the government, large-scale farmers, and agribusinesses, and the products were recognised by the government and included in the normative documents, while attracting a new round of investment from state-owned capital. Nowadays, Heda Technology&#39;s digital agriculture service has been successful in Xinjiang, and is ready to expand the market in Central Asia and the Middle East to help the construction of ‘One Belt, One Road’. From the lack of market recognition to the acceptance of government customers, and then from the government to buy the acceptance of farmers, HeDa  Technology has been from the government, planting farmers, agricultural planting enterprises and other subjects of the recognition, for us to show the country to support the power of agricultural technology enterprises to obtain the legitimacy of the survival of the marketing way.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《组织营销》、《创业营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合法性视角下的2G和2B营销策略及路径；合法性理论的发展沿革；组织合法性的分类；组织合法性的营销作用；合法性视角下的营销策略；合法性视角下的营销策略动因；合法性视角下的营销路径；国际化企业的营销环境；国际化企业的营销策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
